- Assertion: Only friend entries returned, ignored filtered out
- Key line 2001-2004:
  ```typescript
  {
    guid: 0xaan,
    flags: 0x02,  // IGNORED flag
    note: "ignored person",
  }
  ```
- Verify only guid 0x99n is in getFriends() result (line 2010-2012)

**Test 3: SMSG_CONTACT_LIST triggers name queries (Lines 2021-2074)**
- Pattern: Sends contact list, waits for async name query request
- Key lines 2051-2058:
  ```typescript
  const nameQueries = ws.captured.filter(
    (p) => p.opcode === GameOpcode.CMSG_NAME_QUERY,
  );
  const match = nameQueries.find((p) => {
    const r = new PacketReader(p.body);
    return r.uint32LE() === 0x99;
  });
  expect(match).toBeDefined();
  ```
- Then injects SMSG_NAME_QUERY_RESPONSE (lines 2060-2063)
- Verifies friend.name is populated (line 2067)

